name: Warung makan apit kuta
address: H95P+GHW, Tembuku, Bangli Regency, Bali 80671, Indonesia
review 1:
A wonderful spot for lunch, with amazing views and a great atmosphere. The Lemon Iced Tea was very refreshing on a hot afternoon, and the food was very flavoursome.

I would highly recommend a visit as it was authentic, and the service was very friendly.
review 2:
Small Warung next to the Waterfall.
Kind man running it, Juice for 25k and nasi goreng for 25k totally fine for bring close to the Waterfall.
review 3: Very good place. The food is sooo goood. Yoga, the owner and waiter is helpful and informative. It is near a waterfall (cleanest waterfall have seen so far).
review 4: Great food, had fried chicken and mi goreng. 88k with juices. The place is beautiful and the owners are really nice.
review 5: It was the best banana pancake I ever had ! Nice and chill place, the green coco is just cut from the tree, thank you~~

name: Warung Babi Guling Pangkung Sari
